modules.description: @class CardManifest  UI5 independent implementation of a CardManifest reader.  Usage Sample with translation  1. Load the Manifest Json 2. Create Instance var myCardManifest = new CardManifest(oManifestJson); 3. Create and Register a Translator myCardManifest.get("sap.card/i18n"); //load the resource bundle in the given language and create a translator object //   the object only needs to implement getText(sKey) which returns the value. myCardManifest.registerTranslator(oTranslator); 4. Get the title myCardManifest.get("sap.card/title")
